data.description: Step into a freshly renovated first-floor condo with no stairs! Featuring brand-new waterproof luxury vinyl flooring, fresh two-toned paint, and modern enhancements! From top-of-the-line Samsung appliances to a cutting-edge smart thermostat, plus an elegantly tiled shower, no detail has been overlooked! Bask in the inviting glow of the decorative fireplace tiles and enjoy peace of mind with a new water heater. Additional upgrades include enhanced baseboards, chic fixtures, a new toilet, and new cabinetry! Community perks such as pools, spas, and tennis/basketball courts elevate the experience to a resort-like paradise. Welcome to your tranquil and chic contemporary sanctuary!
